    "description": "Devyani International is actively seeking a talented and motivated Hotel Manager to join our dynamic team in Mumbai. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Devyani International:\nDevyani International is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Devyani International!",
